title: Codex (FusionEra 2k25 National Level Competition Organized by Dr.J.J.Magdum College of Engineering , Jaysingpur)
description: The competition consists of three rounds: the first round emphasizes competitive and rapid problem-solving, the second round tests participants' debugging skills, and the final round challenges teams to build an AI-powered quiz generator.

title: TECHTRENDT 2K25 National Level Competition Organized by Dr.J.J.Magdum College of Engineering, Jaysingpur
description: This round tests participants' DSA skills through coding problems focused on logic, efficiency, and core concepts like arrays, strings, trees, graphs, and dynamic programming.

title: QUIZ Competition based on C and Python Organized by Dr.J.J.Magdum College of Engineering , Jaysingpur
description: The round features MCQs on C and Python, covering syntax, data types, control flow, functions, pointers, OOP (in Python), and standard libraries to assess both theoretical and practical understanding.

title: Code Crusade (@NimBus 2k25 National Level Competition Organized by Sanjay Ghowdawat Institude)
description: The competition consists of three rounds: the first round focuses on individual debugging tasks, the second round involves both debugging and a hide-and-seek-style challenge with my partner, and the final round requires participants to collaboratively solve complex problems.

title: Lakshya 3.0 2K25 National Level Competition Organized by Dr.J.J.Magdum College of Engineering , Jaysingpur
description: The competition has three rounds: an aptitude round testing logical and quantitative skills, a technical round assessing core programming knowledge, and a group discussion evaluating communication, teamwork, and idea presentation.
